  "title": "Driver",
  "description": "<p>1. A valid Class 3 / 4 licence, familiar driving a 14 foot lorry and 20 foot lorry with at least 3 years of driving experience.</p><p>2. A clean driving record and familiarity with Singapore Map.</p><p>3. Daily picking up of foreign workers from dormitory to working site. End of the day, send them back to their dormitory.</p><p>4. Day and night shift. Required to work on Sunday and Public Holidays.</p><p>5. Running errands or delivering materials.</p><p>6. Collection of payments.</p><p>7. Maintaining the vehicle safe and clean.</p>",
